---
title: HelloHero: Peppercorn Lamb Rump with Veggie Fries & Cucumber Salad
description: You know you’re in for a good night when the only thing standing between you and this classy lamb dish is amatter of minutes. With only the most tender lamb rump cut, a punchy pepper crusting and baked veggie fries,you just can't go wrong.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
